abstract: "Zara is a persistent, evolving AI engineering partner built on Model Context Protocol. It combines 3-layer cognitive memory with semantic embeddings, multi-agent orchestration (10 agents), 132-signal skill routing, and self-improving reflection loops to deliver an AI companion that remembers, learns, and grows with the developer."
